  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >My SuperMarket is a third-person simulation game in which you, as a member of a team of up to 4 people, own a supermarket in the middle of the city. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is your responsibility to manage the supermarket, organize and serve the customers while expanding and making the most profit you can. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CUSTOMIZE YOUR SUPERMARKET</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1244910/extras/8d555b908173ce1730ca50c9da8d0697.avif?t=1769515272\" width=616 height=148 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy new objects, place them where you want, rotate, align, you name it. Your supermarket, your rules. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from a catalog of items ranging from the standard ones needed to sell products in your supermarket to slot machines, frames, plants, and more. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ORDER PRODUCTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1244910/extras/102674bf43a5b5d7e7c1a3d3852a9d66.avif?t=1769515272\" width=616 height=148 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Order products and have them delivered to your store and placed on your shelves. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage your warehouse products and get them whenever you need them. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEEP SHELVES FILLED</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1244910/extras/ff4422d383c3562f45aac998f521edbc.avif?t=1769515272\" width=616 height=148 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After delivery, your job is to restock the shelves with enough products to keep your customers happy. Remember, a happy customer is a returning customer. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SERVE YOUR CUSTOMERS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1244910/extras/e87a76d8ab4ec571220a5e10e025d82f.avif?t=1769515272\" width=616 height=148 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Keep an eye on your cash register and don't keep customers waiting too long, they won't be very happy if you do. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEEP STORE CLEAN</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1244910/extras/7ef803a92e43dd47e38d94da831397c5.avif?t=1769515272\" width=616 height=148 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some customers throw trash on the floor, others have dirty shoes. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try to keep your store as clean as possible because customers don't like dirty places. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DIFFERENT EVENTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1244910/extras/9d6588495881f6aee62ec54a83fdfa97.avif?t=1769515272\" width=616 height=148 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deal with different types of events. From customers who steal or are in a hurry, to a bus that has several customers eager to get some products off the shelves and be served. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UNLOCK PRODUCTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1244910/extras/bdb43fed8f7188f5724c46f479019488.avif?t=1769515272\" width=616 height=148 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get more reputation as you go. More reputation means more products to choose from. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Try to keep your reputation and more importantly your bank balance positive! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HIRE STAFF</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1244910/extras/c8db5083f7258caa736e2b51519fe68c.avif?t=1769515272\" width=616 height=148 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Need help with the store? No problem! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hire staff and make them work for you! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PLAY WITH FRIENDS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1244910/extras/aeffd4b97607e2c279447c1a53005c6a.avif?t=1769515272\" width=616 height=148 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >How would you manage your supermarket when it gets too big? Friends! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Invite your friends to the lobby and play with them. Don't forget to hit each other :)</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >My SuperMarket is a third-person simulation game in which you, as a member of a team of up to 4 people, own a supermarket in the middle of the city. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is your responsibility to manage the supermarket, organize and serve the customers while expanding and making the most profit you can. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CUSTOMIZE YOUR SUPERMARKET</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1244910/extras/8d555b908173ce1730ca50c9da8d0697.avif?t=1769515272\" width=616 height=148 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy new objects, place them where you want, rotate, align, you name it. Your supermarket, your rules. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from a catalog of items ranging from the standard ones needed to sell products in your supermarket to slot machines, frames, plants, and more. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ORDER PRODUCTS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1244910/extras/102674bf43a5b5d7e7c1a3d3852a9d66.avif?t=1769515272\" width=616 height=148 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Order products and have them delivered to your store and placed on your shelves. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage your warehouse products and get them whenever you need them. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEEP SHELVES FILLED</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1244910/extras/ff4422d383c3562f45aa